Congredi `Our Documentation <//congredi.github.io/congredi/>`__
===============================================================

    Peered Democratic Documents

    For the static webclient written in JS, see
    `delegito.io <//delegito.io>`__

``Congredi`` is a python program that allows a community to help
individuals write changes to repositories of text, that are then voted
on by organizations to find a consensus.

Think that's useful? Give it a try! If you have any feature requests or
questions, hop on over to gitter &
`waffle <https://waffle.io/congredi/congredi>`__. I'm looking for
contributors on some issues.

|Stories in Ready| |Stories in Progress| |Code Triagers Badge|

The build status is misleading, if you've got python 2.7, it should
work.
